reviewText: Lovely set of songs in high definition. The Ernest Ranglin is one of my favorites.
Dr. AIX forgot to mention that you need to spend $50 to get this dvd for free!!! Or buy it for $25

I'm the producer of this particular demonstration disc (done 5 years ago in conjunction with Intel) and thought people here would want to know that we give this disc away for free at our AIX Records website.
